title: 'Oooh... I'm so scared', crown prince says of Annuar Musa
text:
More 
Johor crown prince Tunku Ismail Sultan Ibrahim offered a sarcastic response when asked if he was afraid of his rival Umno information chief Annuar Musa with regard to the contest for the Football Association of Malaysia (FAM) president post. 
“Oooh... I am so scared,” he quipped with a smile when one of the audience asked him this. 
The crown prince was speaking to fans of the national football team at the Grand Hyatt hotel in Kuala Lumpur.
